Logged tonight, decided to take it easy and started a small charm kite.  Mob stuck to charmee, could not get it away with full 4 dots and assonance.  Didn't originally notice until after a few pulls and thought 'hang on, I'm not having to run around lots'.  Then I remembered someone else mentioned this (I think).<br>
Don't know what's changed, but has anyone else noticed this? or am I just imagining it.<br>
<br>
