Had a few comments aggro kiting in the past with necro and bst in Nadox about being able to keep aggro nicely.  1 and a half rounds of chants and the necro just couldn't get the mob off me.  Also spent a lot of time in HoH too.  Was usefull when there were 2 mobs and people started targetting both, I could get aggro back onto me very quickly.<br>
No more I guess.<br>
(Suspect there'll be an AA soon to get back the ability we once had).<br>
Thinking about this further, I could see why it was changed.  We've mentioned on the boards alot of times that we can tank/keep aggro fairly easily with our chants, and I guess bards were never meant to be able todo this, thus the change.<br>
<br>
